Package: comts
Title: Comts: A pipeline for estimating the gene abundance in microbial community.
Version: 0.99.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Xiang", "Zhou", , "zhouxiang221@mails.ucas.ac.cn", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0009-0000-7886-4659"))
Description: To calculate the gene abundance in microbial community (GAM,%). This package will use fastp, seqkit, and diamond, which are biosoftware that exists in the Linux environment, so it needs to be run in a Linux environment.
